net.sf.tweety.arg.prob.test.deductive

Class DeductiveProbabilisticKnowledgebase

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.tweety.arg.prob.test.deductive.DeductiveProbabilisticKnowledgebase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    net.sf.tweety.commons.BeliefBase

    public class DeductiveProbabilisticKnowledgebase
extends Object
implements net.sf.tweety.commons.BeliefBase
    This class represents a probabilistic knowledge base in the sense of [Hunter, Thimm, 2013, in preparation]. It consists of a (possibly inconsistent) set of propositional formulas (ie. a deductive knowledge base) and a set of probability assignments to some set of formulas.
    Author:
    Matthias Thimm
